Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:06.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,Six, seven, eight, nine, ten, eleven, twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's not that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:10.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:13.27,Spike,,0,0,0,,How are you supposed to read twelve books in one weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:15.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia obviously thinks I can
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:17.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,or she would never ever assign them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:19.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm not planning on letting her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:22.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope you're not planning on sleeping then either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:24.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Actually, Spike, why don't you take the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:25.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:26.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This books are gonna keep me busy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:33.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,I do have a long list of things I've been dying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:36.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Touch nose with tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:39.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:41.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,Play bongos on my belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:43.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:45.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,Smell my dirty feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:49.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:54.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,That didn't take nearly as long as I thought it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:37.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,What to do, what to do…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.61,Spike,,0,0,0,,A hot air balloon ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:48.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:50.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:51.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Runaway balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:56.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:23.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,That was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:27.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,If I didn't know better,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:29.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,I would swear that I was in the middle of the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,dark and scary Everfree Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:37.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,Come on Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:41.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,just because this forest is full of wild, dangerous animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean that you gonna see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.40,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come 'n' get me, ya big goons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm running! I'm running!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wow, Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,I mean, you rocketed those boulders at them like they were… rockets!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,You saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.25,Spike,,0,0,0,,You… saved my life…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come on, we should be heading on back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.71,Spike,,0,0,0,,Man, am I lucky you were out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,Why were you out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.72,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Saw a balloon floating by with nopony in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Came out here to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:07.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Guess you did too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:13.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,Uh… yeah… I was investigating the runaway hot air balloon too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:17.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,So… now as the mystery's been solved, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:26.16,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Thanks for walking me home, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.66,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That was mighty kind of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but now I have some chores that need tending to, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.33,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.86,Spike,,0,0,0,,What chores? I'll do them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:34.00,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's sweet, but you don't have…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.17,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's the least I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.17,Spike,,0,0,0,,You saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,I need to repay the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:38.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Shoot, Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,that's what friends do for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:42.35,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You don't need to repay the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yes I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sugar, it's okay, it's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.99,Spike,,0,0,0,,Applejack, you don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:49.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,This is something I really need to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:53.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd hate to get in the way of doing something you need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,Great! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:58.97,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Applebloom is over yonder giving little Piggington a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:02.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I was gonna lend her a hoof, but maybe you could lend her one instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:03.61,Spike,,0,0,0,,On the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,Applejack said I could help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.59,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Great! I could use all the help I can get!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:17.32,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wait 'til Applejack sees how you sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Good job, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:26.15,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Applejack, is it okay if I get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:28.34,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna be late for my Crusaders meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.41,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We're getting fitted for water skis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You definitely don't wanna be late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:36.74,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Water skiing cutiemark, here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:38.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Spike, you can head on out too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:42.34,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I reckon you have repaid me in full, so we're officially even-steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:42.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,We're not even close to being even-steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.09,Spike,,0,0,0,,Please, Applejack,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,you must allow me to assist you further.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Just don't feel right to have you doing things for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:54.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:54.64,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Really, you don't…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:55.79,Spike,,0,0,0,,Pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.73,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's just not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.27,Spike,,0,0,0,,Pretty pretty pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:02.92,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.94,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You can help Granny Smith and me bake some…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,Pies! Pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm helping Applejack make some pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.45,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Spike, little feller,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.75,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,can you get us some more eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Applejack,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,let me get something to clean that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:44.80,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Appreciate all your help today, sugar cube, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I can take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,It is my honor and my duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,today is just the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:51.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What's that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:53.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,You saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:56.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,According to the Spike the Dragon code,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,I owe you a life debt and must serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.99,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Now what about Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:03.50,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Doesn't she need your help and such?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:07.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'd better break the news to Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,I just hope she doesn't take it too hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:11.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,Be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.72,Spike,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:24.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,This is your personal moral ethical dragon code we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,You have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.72,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's not like you and Twilight won't be friends anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:30.99,Spike,,0,0,0,,but it won't be the same…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:32.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,But it has to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight, Applejack just saved my life
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.12,Spike,,0,0,0,,from horrible dragon-eating timberwolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.49,Spike,,0,0,0,,And, as you are aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,I adhere to my dragon code
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:48.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,and this means I must serve her for the rest of my natural born days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:54.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's… been an honor…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,being your faithful assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:07.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,She said it was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.15,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:13.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,So, with Twilight's blessing, I'm free to follow my code and serve you until...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,well, until
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,FOREVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.68,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Listen, sugarcube
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:30.73,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I completely respect your dragon code…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:32.36,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,truly I do, but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:35.41,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I just can't cope with you permanently serving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,Please, Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.08,Spike,,0,0,0,,My dragon code is a part of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:41.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,I have to be true to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.74,Spike,,0,0,0,,If you don't let me do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:45.08,Spike,,0,0,0,,I won't be a noble dragon anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:46.73,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:50.29,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I can't have you feeling like you're not a noble dragon now, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,Great! Then from here on in,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:54.49,Spike,,0,0,0,,your wish is my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:01.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I would like you to…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.11,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Help me take some of the pie you made to…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:14.91,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.17,Spike,,0,0,0,,I helped bake it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:44.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,You even look good when you're chewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:47.17,Spike,,0,0,0,,Who looks good when they're chewing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna have some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I had a big lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's ten in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Breakfast. A big breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:01.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Maybe you could take her plate back to the kitchen and wash it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:03.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:09.35,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I saved Spike from some timberwolves in the Everfree Forest and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,now he thinks he has to serve me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.92,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, what I wouldn't give to have somepony forever in my debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:20.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'd get them to organize my closets and give me pedicures and and help me with my sewing, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:24.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Okay I get it. Having somepony to do things for you would be a dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:27.82,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But I don't feel right having Spike thinking he owes me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:32.22,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You tasted that pie. Sometimes his help isn't that helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:36.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,Do you… have a broom I could borrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,AJ, Rarity, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.97,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Applejack saved Spike's life and now he has to serve her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:51.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What are you having him do? Wash your laundry? Clean your room? Help you with your unfinished novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:54.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Mine's about about this awesome pegasus, who's the best flyer ever
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:56.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and becomes the captain of the Wonderbolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:11:01.31,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How ever did you come up with this ingeniously woven intricate plotline?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:02.69,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:05.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Thing is, I don't really want him to serve me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:07.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But I don't know how to get him to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.83,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:12.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just make him help you with something really really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I don't want him to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:19.20,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Puh-lease. He'll quit way before there is even a chance of getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:22.58,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So… Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Applejack was gonna help me stack some hay
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,so I could practice smashing through it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,but I'm feeling extra extra powerful today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:33.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:35.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:39.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, instead of hay, I'm gonna smash through rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.09,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah! A huge tower of rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And you're gonna build it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:48.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I mean, unless you don't wanna help Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:51.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,I do! It's Spike's dragon code!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Then get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:57.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Trust me. This is gonna work like a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:05.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I was sure he'd give up after, like, three rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.27,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:10.10,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,If it had been me, I'd just have pretended I didn't have anything for him to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:12.10,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,Is this high enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:17.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's plenty high. Come on down, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:20.98,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Bad news, he actually ended up building a whole rock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:21.94,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Good news…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:27.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I've got a rock tower to knock down…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:30.42,Spike,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,That... was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:40.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.93,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wanna do it again, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,Applejack will rebuild it for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:47.86,Spike,,0,0,0,,And when I say "Applejack", I of course mean "me".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:50.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:51.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:56.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't think Rainbow Dash needs anymore of your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,My help, she doesn't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:00.13,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Right, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:01.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:03.81,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,, I guess I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:05.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:06.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:09.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I just can't think of one more thing I need help with, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,you don't have to do anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:15.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you can't think of anything else I can help with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:16.66,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Exactly that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:19.80,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else. I don't want you to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:23.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,If I don't help you, how I know I'm a noble dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:24.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:27.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's things you need help with, that you don't even realize you need help with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:30.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,If she needed help, I think she'd realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:35.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe Applejack needs help realizing what she needs help with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,Like, maybe your back itches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.92,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That does feel good…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:42.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,See? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,you might need help remembering your favorite song:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:47.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dragon is the finest creature ever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:50.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's more to them than just guarding treasure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.84,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's her favorite s…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,Or, you might need help breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.24,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Breathing? I certainly do not…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,There are plenty of things I can help you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:04.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,And you don't even have to trouble yourself with thinking of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:07.03,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,No, I'll think of them. Let me think of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:14.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Twilight, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.37,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't mean to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, it's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I need to take a break anyway. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:30.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I know Spike told you he was gonna follow his dragon code
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:33.13,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and serve me forever for saving him from the timberwolves,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.44,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and that you are okay with it, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wait... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,He said he told you all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:44.00,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing maybe you were a little distracted when he told ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:48.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Should have realized you wouldn't let him go so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:51.48,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, now that you know what's going on, maybe you could talk some sense into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:53.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, Applejack, I wish I could, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:55.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,this is dragon code we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:58.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Surely you know how important the dragon code is to a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:00.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'm starting to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:04.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's the only one other way Spike is gonna fulfill the debt he feels he owes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:13.04,Spike,,0,0,0,,Seventy, seventy one, seventy two, seventy three, seventy four, seventy five…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,All right, y'all. Here's the deal:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:17.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Spike needs to save my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:21.23,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And you want us to… shoot you out of a cannon towards a hornet's nest and give Spike a butterfly net,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:25.46,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,so he can catch you mere seconds before you hit the nest and are struck by a thousand angry hornets!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:27.99,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'll wear this moustache.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:32.39,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,No! I am gonna be attacked by a timberwolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:36.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Can I still wear the moustache?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:44.46,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,When I give the signal, Pinkie Pie and Rarity will come run out of the wood
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,being pursued by the timberwolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:49.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'll start to run too, but then pretend to give my hoof stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:51.62,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'll ask Spike to help me dislodge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:55.60,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And he will, and I will able to get away from the terrifying timberwolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:59.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Having saved me from a certain doom, Spike will then consider us even.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:00.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Everybody get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.38,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Just one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:10.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.75,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:17.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We're all ready to take our parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:21.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But are you sure you're ready to play yours, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:25.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Show us your best damsel in distress move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:29.94,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:34.14,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Absolutely horrendous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:36.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Okay, this needs some serious work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:41.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now first we must lift your foreleg up to your forehead, like so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,No time! Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.62,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Over here, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,You said you have something else for me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:51.78,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yes, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:56.33,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I was just hoping you could maybe sweep up all these leaves for a compost pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.62,Spike,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:05.86,Spike,,0,0,0,,By the way, there are exactly 24 million 567 thousand 8 hundred and 37 blades of grass at Sweet Apple Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:09.10,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you counted every single one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:14.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,You asked me to! And as a noble dragon, and follower of my dragon code, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.66,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,That was very convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:23.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,TIMBERWOLVES!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:27.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We're DOOOMED!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:33.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,See? Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:18:00.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I seemed to have my hoof caught in-between two rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:02.29,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I cannot run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:05.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I am a… damsel in distress!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:07.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Help me, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:11.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,No, no, don't wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:20.66,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Save me from a terrifying timberwolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:24.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, it would be terrifying if it wasn't a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:27.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,You got the clopping of his claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,The roar was spot-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,And the detail on his face is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:35.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,But you forgot one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:38.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,His breath. You can smell a real timberwolf's breath from a mile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:43.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,Too late. I'm already on…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:46.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Timberwolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:53.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,Timberwolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,Applejack, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I can't! I'm really stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:25.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,No more messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:30.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.03,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.32,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Forget it, Spike. You got to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:46.34,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Would you just forget your dragon code already and go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:48.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:50.42,Spike,,0,0,0,,I have to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:58.08,Spike,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What happened to you guys back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:18.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thought you were right behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:21.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,My hoof was stuck and then that timberwolf was coming right at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Wait! You were actually stuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:28.99,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But Spike picked up a pebble and rocketed that thing right into huge timberwolf's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:32.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It was something, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:35.90,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,'Course, I wouldn't have needed help
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:39.73,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,if I haven't been trying to stage a fake timberwolf attack in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.49,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:45.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I know this code thing is important to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:47.97,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but if something like this comes up in the future…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:50.36,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Think maybe we'll go be back to my code, say
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:53.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,"That's what friends do", and leave it at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:55.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I promise I won't think of you as any less noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.84,Spike,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:03.81,Spike,,0,0,0,,But, maybe, let's just try to avoid the situations
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.81,Spike,,0,0,0,,where one of us actually needs the other one to save his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You got yourself a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:19.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:20.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,Happy to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't know what I'd do without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:27.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,No really! I'm really really really happy to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.76,Somepony,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVIY PONETS
